00:14:19,500 --> 00:14:26,500
Your land, air, and hunting grounds are more important.

145
00:14:27,000 --> 00:14:34,500
You must watch over it more than your own homes where you sleep.

146
00:14:35,000 --> 00:14:37,500
Keep it cleaned up.

147
