Except to us who live in the land.

153
00:15:11,000 --> 00:15:15,500
Those things that must be cleaned and watched over

154
00:15:15,600 --> 00:15:22,000
We should only put them on ourselves, not pass them to another person.

155
00:15:23,000 --> 00:15:26,000
As we are not careful of ourselves

156
00:15:26,500 --> 00:15:32,000
And as we do not instruct our young people to
respectfully use that [land]

157
00:15:32,500 --> 00:15:38,000
We’re making it become like that because we hide
[the knowledge] from our young people.

158
