179
00:17:57,000 --> 00:18:07,000
These days, you see, I saw people getting paid to clean up the land
over there.

180
00:18:07,900 --> 00:18:10,000
And yet, they’re called cleaners.

181
00:18:10,100 --> 00:18:13,000
Now, they only have their eyes on money.

182
00:18:13,800 --> 00:18:18,500
Back then, however, our ancestors didn’t watch for [money].

183
00:18:20,000 --> 00:18:27,000
Our ancestors back then only looked out for living long lives.

184
00:18:30,000 --> 00:18:32,000
They were like this:

