It’s like that depriving us of everything.

237
00:24:11,000 --> 00:24:17,000
And the pollution is depriving food of our hunting and gathering grounds.

238
00:24:17,500 --> 00:24:25,000
That ability to speak English will not save us, only our belief

239
00:24:25,500 --> 00:24:30,000
And cleaning up our land out of respect through faith.

240
00:24:30,500 --> 00:24:37,800
You see, this is how our ancestors back then treated this land
that they used:

241
00:24:38,500 --> 00:24:42,000
They would respect even the wilderness as their own houses.

242
00:24:42,500 --> 00:24:53,000
And then, they also respecting the Kuskokwim, their water where they
